      <title>渣打银行首席执行官温特斯警告美国财政政策增加债务买家罢工的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/winters-warns-us-fiscal-policy-raises-risk-of-debt-buyer-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行首席执行官比尔·温特斯表示，由于政界人士未能控制该国不断膨胀的赤字，美国面临着投资者冷落其债务的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/winters-warns-us-fiscal-policy-raises-risk-of-debt-buyer-strike</guid>
