    <item>
      <title>中国淡化2024年大规模刺激措施，考验投资者耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-downplays-big-stimulus-in-2024-testing-investor-patience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李强发出了迄今为止最明确的信号，即在数十年来最严重的通缩浪潮中，北京不会采取大规模刺激措施来重振增长。另一批令人不安的数据正在考验那些担心北京方面落后了的投资者的耐心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-downplays-big-stimulus-in-2024-testing-investor-patience</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Villeroy 表示现在知道欧洲央行 2024 年何时降息还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/ecb-rate-cuts-villeroy-says-premature-to-say-when-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行政策制定者弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛 (Francois Villeroy de Galhau) 表示，现在判断该机构将于 2024 年何时开始降息还为时过早，因为该决定将由数据指导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/ecb-rate-cuts-villeroy-says-premature-to-say-when-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:27:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国提高利率并引入爬行钉住汇率制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行提高了关键利率，并为当地货币引入了爬行钉住汇率制度，以遏制顽固的通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政司司长表示香港不会征收离境税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/hong-kong-won-t-impose-departure-tax-says-finance-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港财政司司长陈茂波表示，他没有计划向居民征收离境税，拒绝了旨在缓解政府不断扩大的赤字的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/hong-kong-won-t-impose-departure-tax-says-finance-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:52:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及货币大幅贬值的押注因国际货币基金组织加大一揽子计划的希望而破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bets-on-big-fx-devaluation-in-egypt-crushed-as-government-nears-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于埃及政府即将与国际货币基金组织(IMF)达成协议以扩大救助计划的规模，交易员们纷纷在今年年初解除对埃及货币大幅贬值的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bets-on-big-fx-devaluation-in-egypt-crushed-as-government-nears-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达沃斯直播：布林肯暗示今年将举行拜登-习近平会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在世界经济论坛上向与会者表示，今年美国和中国领导人之间的接触将更加频繁，这对国际贸易来说可能是一个好兆头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/davos-live-global-elite-braces-for-some-argentine-showmanship</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 07:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
